    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Here is a quick list of small optimisations I've already made\n- Imported all scripts from CDN js-deliver (so we can merge them)\n- Custom build of boostrap.js with only the collapse component.\n- Custom font with font-icons (5 icons)\n- Removed all boostrap unused import in scss\n- Deferred script at the bottom and optimized loading sequence\n- Leanified all assets https://github.com/JayXon/Leanify it use svgo but also optimize other format ( I had to revert one icon so I don't like no more the idea of build script )\n\nIdeas\n- Dust css or similar (the website is simple the parser should be ok)\n- some fixes in sass for overqualified selector\n- an illustration of the doc is still in png\n- include more svg, so less call but bigger html\n\n@vvo I'm not sure to understand the sprite.png? If you want to convert svg in png it's a bad idea.\n",
